{
  "stem": "11174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, it's like a document to be able to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to be-- go out a certain time according to your paper and come back in a certain time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was quite a little-- much different already-- more restricted but not direct [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] discrimination.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we Jews, they didn't want us to call it ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Japanese were against it-- just a restricted area of some sort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no-- Chinese people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big, big city with millions of-- [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this, there were also Chinese living there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they say up to here you can go and from here, you know, except with a permit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were there-- there was some people did some business, some people did some work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- and then we-- we got-- well at first, the yeshiva got.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were giving some aids from the Polish consulate that was in the beginning together under the protection of the English.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then there was no more, and some they came still, I think, through London from the Polish government as Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then after a while, it was pretty hard because the Joint Distribution didn't have any direct route to send money from America because there was war between Japan and America.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these-- the-- the same committee-- they were Russian Jews mostly in Shanghai-- the Russian Jews means those Jews that settled in Shanghai after the-- the Russian Revolution went away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were already settled there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some are rich.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some are middle class.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So some of the rich people-- as we understood and heard-- lent money to the Joint Distribution committee secretly because Japan would not have liked it.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
